YOUR MEMORY IN THE PROPER WAY.

222
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:59,400
- I THOUGHT IT WAS ABOUT TIME
FOR YOU TO SHOW UP, BIG DADDY.

223
00:17:00,166 --> 00:17:02,433
